FBIS3-58332 "drweu008_h_94007" FBIS-WEU-94-008 Document Type:Daily Report 12 Jan 1994 GERMANY Former SED Official Denies Paying Zhirinovskiy AU1101142194 Cologne Deutschlandfunk Network in German 1200 GMT 11 Jan 94 AU1101142194 Cologne Deutschlandfunk Network Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] [Werner] Girke, the former administrator of the foreign assets of the Socialist Unity Party of Germany [SED], has denied having forwarded funds to Russian nationalist Zhirinovskiy. In an interview with STERN, Girke stated that he met incidentally with Zhirinovskiy in Austria shortly before Christmas. He also rejected the accusation concerning embezzled SED assets. In fact, he said, over 53 million German marks [DM] have been transferred to accounts held on trust. Another DM6 million will follow shortly.
